Cléopatre 7 Théa Philopator kɛ ɖoo lɔŋ taa [[Egipiti (Égypte)|Egipiti]] tʊ, ɛ-kɛkɛ peɖe tɛ abiɖe. Ɛɛkɛ Ptɔlɛmɛ cejewiye taa tʊ. Palʊlɩ-ɩ efemiye hiu nɛ naalɛ kɛ kɩyɛɛna fenaɣ taa kɛ pɩnaɣ 30 nɛ pɩcɔ palʊʊlʊ Yeesu Krɩstu kɛ Alɛxandrɩ tɛtʋ taa. Ɛ-caa kɛlɛ Ptɔlɛmɛ 12 alɛtɛ tʊ, nɛ ɛ-ɖoo payawaɣ sɩse Cléopatre 6 weyi ɛlɛ kɛ Tɩɖɩphɛmɛ tʊ yɔ. Ɛkɛkɛ ɛjaɖɛna niŋɖiyu pɩnzɩ hiŋ kagbanzɩ nɛ kʊyʊm pɩsɩnaɣ pɩnaɣ niidozo mbɩ yɔ. Ɛna ɛɖalaa nɛ ɛwalʊ Ptɔlɛmɛ 13 nɛ Ptɔlɛmɛ 14 paasɩŋna kpelaɣ ɖɔkʊ pɩtasɩnaɣ sɔɔja sɔsɔɔ Roma tʊ weyi payawaɣ-ɩ se Marc Antoine. Pɩkɩlɩ tabalɩyɛ yaa nɛ ɛyɩsɩm mbʊ pʊwɛ ɛnaɣ [[Jules César|Jules César]] pɛhɛkʊ taa yɔ, nɛ Marc Antoine pɔyɔ kɛ patɩlayi. 

